<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to UniNav!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    h1, h2 {
      color: #4f46e5;
    }
    .feature {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      border-left: 3px solid #4f46e5;
    }
    .next-steps {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to UniNav!</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>!</p>
    
    <p>We're excited to welcome you to <strong>UniNav</strong> - your new hub for university study materials and academic resources!</p>
    
    <h2>About UniNav</h2>
    <p>UniNav is a collaborative platform where students can share, discover, and organize academic resources. You've joined the <%= departmentName %> department community!</p>
    
    <div class="feature">
      <h3>ðŸ“š What You Can Do:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Access course materials organized by faculty, department and level</li>
        <li>Upload and share your own study resources</li>
        <li>Bookmark materials and create personal collections</li>
        <li>Write blogs and earn from your academic insights</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="next-steps">
      <h3>ðŸš€ Next Steps:</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Verify your email</strong> by clicking the verification link sent to your inbox</li>
        <li><strong>Complete your profile</strong> by adding your academic interests</li>
        <li><strong>Explore materials</strong> in your department</li>
        <li><strong>Upload your first study resource</strong> to help fellow students</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    
    <a href="https://uninav.com/explore" class="button">Start Exploring</a>
    
    <p>If you have any questions, check out our <a href="https://uninav.com/help">Help Center</a> or contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@uninav.com">support@uninav.com</a>.</p>
    
    <p>Happy studying!</p>
    <p>The UniNav Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> UniNav. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>You're receiving this email because you signed up for UniNav.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
